{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"Kolkata with Wireless&nbsp;Fidelity","content":"<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><a href=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.wordpress.com/2015/02/06/kolkata-with-wireless-fidelity/\"><img data-attachment-id=\"773\" data-permalink=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.wordpress.com/2015/02/06/kolkata-with-wireless-fidelity/dsc_3819/\" data-orig-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/dsc_3819.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"1048,393\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;4.2&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;anirbansaha&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;NIKON D7000&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1423157029&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;anirbansaha.com&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;110&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;640&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0.002&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"DSC_3819\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/dsc_3819.jpg?w=450\" data-large-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/dsc_3819.jpg?w=700\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-773 size-large\" src=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/dsc_3819.jpg?w=700&#038;h=263\" alt=\"DSC_3819\" srcset=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/dsc_3819.jpg?w=700&amp;h=263 700w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/dsc_3819.jpg?w=150&amp;h=56 150w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/dsc_3819.jpg?w=450&amp;h=169 450w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/dsc_3819.jpg?w=768&amp;h=288 768w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/dsc_3819.jpg 1048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\"   /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">The social media (that I&#8217;m connected to) started reverberating with a single fact a few days back.</p>\n<p style=\"padding-left:30px;text-align:justify;\"><strong>Kolkata will soon become WiFi enabled</strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">This was <strong>big </strong>news. Some considered it to be a rumour, since for most, it was too good to be true. The need for internet has been escalating in the last few years. Kolkata needed WiFi. And it was served what it needed.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><!--more--></p>\n<p style=\"padding-left:30px;text-align:justify;\">The 5<sup>th</sup> of February, 2015 was historic.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">I got the chance to be present at the formal launch of the free 4G WiFi provided by Reliance Jio, at Park Street, as a part of Kolkata Bloggers.</p>\n<figure data-shortcode=\"caption\" id=\"attachment_753\" style=\"width: 585px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"753\" data-permalink=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.wordpress.com/2015/02/06/kolkata-with-wireless-fidelity/start/\" data-orig-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/start.png?w=585&#038;h=435\" data-orig-size=\"585,435\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"start\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/start.png?w=585&#038;h=435?w=450\" data-large-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/start.png?w=585&#038;h=435?w=585\" class=\"size-full wp-image-753\" src=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/start.png?w=585&#038;h=435\" alt=\"The stage being set\" width=\"585\" height=\"435\" srcset=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/start.png 585w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/start.png?w=150&amp;h=112 150w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/start.png?w=450&amp;h=335 450w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 585px) 100vw, 585px\" /><figcaption class=\"wp-caption-text\">The stage being set</figcaption></figure>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Having arrived late, I was unable to get a certain privilege 10 bloggers of the <a href=\"http://www.kolkatabloggers.com/\">Kolkata Bloggers</a> team obtained &#8211; WiFi access an hour and a half before the connection was made &#8216;open&#8217; for the public!</p>\n<figure data-shortcode=\"caption\" id=\"attachment_751\" style=\"width: 580px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"751\" data-permalink=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.wordpress.com/2015/02/06/kolkata-with-wireless-fidelity/audience_start/\" data-orig-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/audience_start.png?w=580&#038;h=433\" data-orig-size=\"580,433\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"audience_start\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/audience_start.png?w=580&#038;h=433?w=450\" data-large-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/audience_start.png?w=580&#038;h=433?w=580\" class=\"size-full wp-image-751\" src=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/audience_start.png?w=580&#038;h=433\" alt=\"The audience eagerly waiting for the launch\" width=\"580\" height=\"433\" srcset=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/audience_start.png 580w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/audience_start.png?w=150&amp;h=112 150w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/audience_start.png?w=450&amp;h=336 450w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 580px) 100vw, 580px\" /><figcaption class=\"wp-caption-text\">The audience eagerly waiting for the launch</figcaption></figure>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">The event was inaugurated by the mayor &#8211; Shovan Chatterjee.</p>\n<figure data-shortcode=\"caption\" id=\"attachment_754\" style=\"width: 588px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"754\" data-permalink=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.wordpress.com/2015/02/06/kolkata-with-wireless-fidelity/shovan/\" data-orig-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/shovan.png?w=588&#038;h=437\" data-orig-size=\"588,437\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"shovan\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/shovan.png?w=588&#038;h=437?w=450\" data-large-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/shovan.png?w=588&#038;h=437?w=588\" class=\"size-full wp-image-754\" src=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/shovan.png?w=588&#038;h=437\" alt=\"Shovan Chatterjee\" width=\"588\" height=\"437\" srcset=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/shovan.png 588w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/shovan.png?w=150&amp;h=111 150w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/shovan.png?w=450&amp;h=334 450w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 588px) 100vw, 588px\" /><figcaption class=\"wp-caption-text\">Shovan Chatterjee</figcaption></figure>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Following him, Subrata Mukherjee spoke on the upcoming digital age Kolkata would be entering into.</p>\n<figure data-shortcode=\"caption\" id=\"attachment_755\" style=\"width: 589px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"755\" data-permalink=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.wordpress.com/2015/02/06/kolkata-with-wireless-fidelity/subrata/\" data-orig-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/subrata.png?w=589&#038;h=437\" data-orig-size=\"589,437\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"subrata\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/subrata.png?w=589&#038;h=437?w=450\" data-large-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/subrata.png?w=589&#038;h=437?w=589\" class=\"size-full wp-image-755\" src=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/subrata.png?w=589&#038;h=437\" alt=\"Subrata \" width=\"589\" height=\"437\" srcset=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/subrata.png 589w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/subrata.png?w=150&amp;h=111 150w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/subrata.png?w=450&amp;h=334 450w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 589px) 100vw, 589px\" /><figcaption class=\"wp-caption-text\">Subrata Mukherjee</figcaption></figure>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Mr. Tarun Jhunjhunwala (from Reliance) then spoke about the 4G technology that would encompass the city.</p>\n<figure data-shortcode=\"caption\" id=\"attachment_756\" style=\"width: 562px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"756\" data-permalink=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.wordpress.com/2015/02/06/kolkata-with-wireless-fidelity/jhunjhun/\" data-orig-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/jhunjhun.png?w=562&#038;h=414\" data-orig-size=\"562,414\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"jhunjhun\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/jhunjhun.png?w=562&#038;h=414?w=450\" data-large-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/jhunjhun.png?w=562&#038;h=414?w=562\" class=\"size-full wp-image-756\" src=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/jhunjhun.png?w=562&#038;h=414\" alt=\"Tarun Jhunjhunwala\" width=\"562\" height=\"414\" srcset=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/jhunjhun.png 562w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/jhunjhun.png?w=150&amp;h=110 150w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/jhunjhun.png?w=450&amp;h=331 450w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 562px) 100vw, 562px\" /><figcaption class=\"wp-caption-text\">Tarun Jhunjhunwala</figcaption></figure>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">At this point, let me tell you about the WiFi connection. A misconception has spread that only 4G enabled devices will be able to access this connection. Reliance Jio is equipping the citizens of Kolkata an internet connection that will supply 4G internet speed, but through WiFi, purely. This means that <strong>any </strong>device, that can harness WiFi, can use this connection.</p>\n<figure data-shortcode=\"caption\" id=\"attachment_757\" style=\"width: 587px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"757\" data-permalink=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.wordpress.com/2015/02/06/kolkata-with-wireless-fidelity/night_stage-2/\" data-orig-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/night_stage1.png?w=587&#038;h=433\" data-orig-size=\"587,433\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"night_stage\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/night_stage1.png?w=587&#038;h=433?w=450\" data-large-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/night_stage1.png?w=587&#038;h=433?w=587\" class=\"size-full wp-image-757\" src=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/night_stage1.png?w=587&#038;h=433\" alt=\"The night stage!\" width=\"587\" height=\"433\" srcset=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/night_stage1.png 587w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/night_stage1.png?w=150&amp;h=111 150w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/night_stage1.png?w=450&amp;h=332 450w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 587px) 100vw, 587px\" /><figcaption class=\"wp-caption-text\">The night stage!</figcaption></figure>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Following Mr Jhunjhunwala, the honourable Chief Minister of West Bengal &#8211; Mamata Banerjee &#8211; took the microphone to thank Reliance for their support.This had been a &#8216;secret&#8217; project. During the past two years, optical fibers were laid down throughout the city, and WiFi hotspots were set up in various places in Kolkata. This was possible primarily due to the efforts of Reliance &#8211; and the workers who were employed to do the task.</p>\n<figure data-shortcode=\"caption\" id=\"attachment_760\" style=\"width: 710px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"760\" data-permalink=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.wordpress.com/2015/02/06/kolkata-with-wireless-fidelity/mamataspeaking/\" data-orig-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/mamataspeaking.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"1048,393\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;4&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;anirbansaha&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;NIKON D7000&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1423156344&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;anirbansaha.com&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;70&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;640&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0.0015625&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"mamataspeaking\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/mamataspeaking.jpg?w=450\" data-large-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/mamataspeaking.jpg?w=700\" class=\"size-large wp-image-760\" src=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/mamataspeaking.jpg?w=700&#038;h=263\" alt=\"Mamata Banerjee speaking\" srcset=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/mamataspeaking.jpg?w=700&amp;h=263 700w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/mamataspeaking.jpg?w=150&amp;h=56 150w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/mamataspeaking.jpg?w=450&amp;h=169 450w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/mamataspeaking.jpg?w=768&amp;h=288 768w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/mamataspeaking.jpg 1048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\"   /><figcaption class=\"wp-caption-text\">Mamata Banerjee</figcaption></figure>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">The chief minister then connected to the WiFi network, and posted the first Twitter update with #WiFiKolkata:</p>\n<figure data-shortcode=\"caption\" id=\"attachment_758\" style=\"width: 585px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"758\" data-permalink=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.wordpress.com/2015/02/06/kolkata-with-wireless-fidelity/tweet/\" data-orig-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/tweet.png?w=585&#038;h=378\" data-orig-size=\"585,378\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"tweet\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/tweet.png?w=585&#038;h=378?w=450\" data-large-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/tweet.png?w=585&#038;h=378?w=585\" class=\"wp-image-758 size-full\" src=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/tweet.png?w=585&#038;h=378\" alt=\"The Chief Minister's first tweet using the WiFi connection by Reliance\" width=\"585\" height=\"378\" srcset=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/tweet.png 585w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/tweet.png?w=150&amp;h=97 150w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/tweet.png?w=450&amp;h=291 450w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 585px) 100vw, 585px\" /><figcaption class=\"wp-caption-text\">The Chief Minister&#8217;s first tweets using the WiFi connection by Reliance</figcaption></figure>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">A <strong>huge </strong>round of applause followed when the tweet was made visible on the giant screen!</p>\n<figure data-shortcode=\"caption\" id=\"attachment_759\" style=\"width: 710px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"759\" data-permalink=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.wordpress.com/2015/02/06/kolkata-with-wireless-fidelity/tweetposted/\" data-orig-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/tweetposted.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"1048,393\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;5&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;anirbansaha&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;NIKON D7000&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1423156805&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;anirbansaha.com&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;170&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;640&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0.0004&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"tweetposted\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/tweetposted.jpg?w=450\" data-large-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/tweetposted.jpg?w=700\" class=\"wp-image-759 size-large\" src=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/tweetposted.jpg?w=700&#038;h=263\" alt=\"When the tweets were posted\" srcset=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/tweetposted.jpg?w=700&amp;h=263 700w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/tweetposted.jpg?w=150&amp;h=56 150w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/tweetposted.jpg?w=450&amp;h=169 450w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/tweetposted.jpg?w=768&amp;h=288 768w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/tweetposted.jpg 1048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\"   /><figcaption class=\"wp-caption-text\">When the tweets were posted</figcaption></figure>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">The audience was notified that the WiFi would be made available for the public at 6:00 PM.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Reliance Jio demonstrated the WiFi speeds on the giant screen.</p>\n<figure data-shortcode=\"caption\" id=\"attachment_761\" style=\"width: 534px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"761\" data-permalink=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.wordpress.com/2015/02/06/kolkata-with-wireless-fidelity/speedmeasure/\" data-orig-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/speedmeasure.png?w=534&#038;h=383\" data-orig-size=\"534,383\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"speedmeasure\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/speedmeasure.png?w=534&#038;h=383?w=450\" data-large-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/speedmeasure.png?w=534&#038;h=383?w=534\" class=\"size-full wp-image-761\" src=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/speedmeasure.png?w=534&#038;h=383\" alt=\"Speed test by Ookla\" width=\"534\" height=\"383\" srcset=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/speedmeasure.png 534w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/speedmeasure.png?w=150&amp;h=108 150w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/speedmeasure.png?w=450&amp;h=323 450w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 534px) 100vw, 534px\" /><figcaption class=\"wp-caption-text\">Speed test by Ookla</figcaption></figure>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Kolkata&#8217;s favourite singer/songwriter Anupam Roy took up his guitar and sang two immensely popular songs written by him.</p>\n<figure data-shortcode=\"caption\" id=\"attachment_785\" style=\"width: 477px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"785\" data-permalink=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.wordpress.com/2015/02/06/kolkata-with-wireless-fidelity/img_1131/\" data-orig-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/img_1131.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"3456,5184\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;5.6&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;Canon EOS 600D&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1423158105&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;250&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;100&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0.0125&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"img_1131\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/img_1131.jpg?w=300\" data-large-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/img_1131.jpg?w=467&#038;h=700\" class=\"wp-image-785 size-large\" src=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/img_1131.jpg?w=467&#038;h=700\" alt=\"img_1131\" width=\"467\" height=\"700\" srcset=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/img_1131.jpg?w=467&amp;h=700 467w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/img_1131.jpg?w=934&amp;h=1400 934w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/img_1131.jpg?w=100&amp;h=150 100w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/img_1131.jpg?w=300&amp;h=450 300w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/img_1131.jpg?w=768&amp;h=1152 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 467px) 100vw, 467px\" /><figcaption class=\"wp-caption-text\">Anupam Roy [Photograph by <a href=\"https://asmitanandy.wordpress.com/\">Asmita Nandy</a>]</figcaption></figure>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">The crowd was delighted!</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Dr. Amit Mitra ended the event with a note of thanks.</p>\n<figure data-shortcode=\"caption\" id=\"attachment_772\" style=\"width: 590px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"772\" data-permalink=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.wordpress.com/2015/02/06/kolkata-with-wireless-fidelity/mitra/\" data-orig-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/mitra.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"1048,1048\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;4.2&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;anirbansaha&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;NIKON D7000&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1423155803&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;anirbansaha.com&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;102&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;640&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0.002&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"mitra\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/mitra.jpg?w=450\" data-large-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/mitra.jpg?w=700\" class=\"wp-image-772\" src=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/mitra.jpg?w=590&#038;h=590\" alt=\"Dr. Sanjay Mitra\" width=\"590\" height=\"590\" srcset=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/mitra.jpg?w=590&amp;h=590 590w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/mitra.jpg?w=150&amp;h=150 150w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/mitra.jpg?w=450&amp;h=450 450w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/mitra.jpg?w=768&amp;h=768 768w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/mitra.jpg?w=700&amp;h=700 700w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/mitra.jpg 1048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\" /><figcaption class=\"wp-caption-text\">Dr. Amit Mitra</figcaption></figure>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:'Courier New';\">If you wish to skip over to the instructions to connect to the WiFi network, click <a href=\"#instructions\">here</a>.</span></p>\n<hr />\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">This was clearly a milestone in the history of Kolkata. <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sahaanirbannew\" target=\"_blank\">Anirban Saha</a>, the lead of <a href=\"http://www.kolkatabloggers.com\" target=\"_blank\">Kolkata Bloggers</a> had posted a question on his Facebook Timeline</p>\n<blockquote><p>What is your take on Wi-Fi enabled Kolkata?</p></blockquote>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">While some were feeling extremely positive about the advent of WiFi throughout the city&#8230;</p>\n<blockquote><p>Its a big step towards digital literacy. People till now who were not sure if they should have mobile data will now enjoy and taste the free service and finally join the digital world. So its a step towards digital literacy for the mass.</p>\n<p>&#8211; Supratik Chatterjee</p></blockquote>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">&#8230;certain people pointed out some different, valid points. I believe two are extremely important.</p>\n<ol style=\"text-align:justify;\">\n<li style=\"padding-left:30px;\">The city doesn&#8217;t really &#8216;need&#8217; WiFi enabled sections as much as it needs a proper drainage system during the rainy season. Calcutta lacks in the fundamental needs of a proper metropolitan, and those requirements should be fulfilled first. Making the city WiFi enabled can be added as the final strokes to a Masterpiece.<br />\n&#8211; Amitendu Maity</li>\n<li style=\"padding-left:30px;\">How efficiently will this work? Currently, the load isn&#8217;t that much, and frankly, handling a single area in Kolkata &#8211; the Park Street region &#8211; is much easier compared to the mayor&#8217;s goal of providing WiFi to Salt Lake, Rajarhat, Barasat &#8211; covering the entire city! How will it hold up in the future?</li>\n</ol>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Apart from these two factors, the question of the day was</p>\n<blockquote><p>How&#8217;s the internet speed?</p></blockquote>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">No one can answer this question. As more and more users connect, we&#8217;ll get to see the outcome. From that day, and from the little we used, it was fine. I&#8217;m including this snippet from <a href=\"http://www.anirbansaha.com/wi-fi-and-kolkata-the-city-of-the-future/\" target=\"_blank\">Anirban Saha&#8217;s Blog</a> to give you a better idea:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">The major skepticism about this Wi-Fi are about the speed it will offer and how free it shall be after a few months. The little that we have used &#8211; seemed fine. Rajya Sabha MP Derek O&#8217;Brien, informed more than 230 routing machines were installed in Park Street itself, each capable of handling 40 machines. That&#8217;s precisely 9200 machines in Park Street alone can access the WiFi without the speed drooping down. While Reliance is keeping tight lipped, insiders in the ruling political party informed me &#8211; freemium model is what is desired. Since this is a cost proposition, Reliance might charge money but not any time soon (might be after Durga Pujas).</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Let&#8217;s hope this works out well. The entire generation of <em>netizens </em>is hoping this 🙂</p>\n<figure data-shortcode=\"caption\" id=\"attachment_766\" style=\"width: 660px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"766\" data-permalink=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.wordpress.com/2015/02/06/kolkata-with-wireless-fidelity/groupfie/\" data-orig-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/groupfie.jpg?w=660&#038;h=371\" data-orig-size=\"960,540\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"groupfie\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/groupfie.jpg?w=660&#038;h=371?w=450\" data-large-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/groupfie.jpg?w=660&#038;h=371?w=700\" class=\"wp-image-766\" src=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/groupfie.jpg?w=660&#038;h=371\" alt=\"The Kolkata Bloggers team with Derek O'Brien\" width=\"660\" height=\"371\" srcset=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/groupfie.jpg?w=660&amp;h=371 660w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/groupfie.jpg?w=150&amp;h=84 150w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/groupfie.jpg?w=450&amp;h=253 450w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/groupfie.jpg?w=768&amp;h=432 768w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/groupfie.jpg?w=700&amp;h=394 700w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/groupfie.jpg 960w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 660px) 100vw, 660px\" /><figcaption class=\"wp-caption-text\">The Kolkata Bloggers team with Derek O&#8217;Brien [from <a href=\"http://souravghosh.com/\">Sourav Ghosh</a>]</figcaption></figure>\n<hr />\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">The WiFi is currently limited to Park Street. It can be used for an indefinite amount of time. Later, certain restrictions may be imposed as to the time or the data usage.</p>\n<div id=\"instructions\" style=\"text-align:justify;\">Finally, here are the instructions to connect to the network:</div>\n<ol style=\"text-align:justify;\">\n<li>Switch on your &#8216;WiFi&#8217;</li>\n<li>Search for networks</li>\n<li>Select <strong>Jio </strong>or <strong>Jionet</strong> (whichever is available) from the list of available connections</li>\n<li>A tab will open on your browser; or, in case it doesn&#8217;t, simply open a browser, and the required tab will appear</li>\n<li>You will see a screen similar to this:\n<p><figure data-shortcode=\"caption\" id=\"attachment_763\" style=\"width: 350px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"763\" data-permalink=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.wordpress.com/2015/02/06/kolkata-with-wireless-fidelity/screenshot_2015-02-05-19-25-03/\" data-orig-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/screenshot_2015-02-05-19-25-03.png?w=350&#038;h=583\" data-orig-size=\"480,800\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Screenshot_2015-02-05-19-25-03\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/screenshot_2015-02-05-19-25-03.png?w=350&#038;h=583?w=270\" data-large-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/screenshot_2015-02-05-19-25-03.png?w=350&#038;h=583?w=420\" class=\"wp-image-763\" src=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/screenshot_2015-02-05-19-25-03.png?w=350&#038;h=583\" alt=\"Ignore the 'invalid phone number' text\" width=\"350\" height=\"583\" srcset=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/screenshot_2015-02-05-19-25-03.png?w=350&amp;h=583 350w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/screenshot_2015-02-05-19-25-03.png?w=90&amp;h=150 90w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/screenshot_2015-02-05-19-25-03.png?w=270&amp;h=450 270w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/screenshot_2015-02-05-19-25-03.png 480w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 350px) 100vw, 350px\" /><figcaption class=\"wp-caption-text\">Ignore the &#8216;invalid phone number&#8217; text</figcaption></figure></li>\n<li>As soon as you submit your phone number, you will receive a text message with your six-digit password.</li>\n<li>Enter the password, and tick the box agreeing to &#8216;Terms and Conditions&#8217;</li>\n<li>You can now use the free WiFi by Reliance</li>\n<li>However,<strong> do not close the Jio tab</strong>. Closing the tab will disconnect you.</li>\n<li>Save your password for logging into the network later.</li>\n</ol>\n<hr />\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:'Courier New';\">For more information on Reliance Jio&#8217;s target on providing WiFi to the whole nation, check this link:  <a href=\"http://www.business-standard.com/article/companies/reliance-jio-to-roll-out-services-in-800-cities-114121700005_1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Reliance Jio to roll out services in 800 cities</a> </span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:'Courier New';\">The photographs used here were obtained from Anirban Saha and the <a href=\"https://twitter.com/Kolkata_Blogger\" target=\"_blank\">twitter page </a>of Kolkata Bloggers.</span></p>\n","date":"2015-02-05T22:26:44.000Z","slug":"kolkata-with-wireless-fidelity","excerpt":"<p>Let&#8217;s hope this works out well. The entire generation of netizens is hoping for this.</p>\n","jetpack_featured_media_url":""},"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":null,"subtitle":null}}},"pageContext":{"id":"b54ffe61-fc81-58b0-9e99-112d7b268386"}}